nt-weight: 700; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 18px;\">Similar Trademarks</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">: Phonetically, visually, or conceptually similar trademarks.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 18px;\">Risk Assessment</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">: The likelihood of conflict or rejection.</span></li></ul></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.06px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 18px;\">Step 5: Refine Your Search</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.06px; text-align: justify;\"><li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">If the tool allows, refine your search by:</span><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Adjusting the similarity threshold.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Focusing on specific classes of goods/services.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Excluding irrelevant results.</span></li></ul></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.06px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 18px;\">Step 6: Consult a Trademark Attorney</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.06px; text-align: justify;\"><li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">While AI tools are 